summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of 5th Avenue West from West Prospect Street to West Highland Drive, all in the City of Seattle by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, all in accordance with Resolution No. 2128 of the city council of the City of Seattle; and providing payment therefor by the mode of "Payment in Bonds", as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle.
